high_descs: Walk straight then hang left and proceed to the edge of the desk with the laptop on it.
Retrieve the tennis racket that is leaning up against the desk.
Turn left and head in the direction of the bed, then hang left and walk to the night stand with the alarm clock and lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the tennis racket.
Pick up the tennis racket on the floor.
Turn left towards the edge of the bed and then turn left towards the green lamp on the desk.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a green lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the side of the desk
Pick up the tennis racket off of the floor
Walk to your left and position yourself so you are facing the small desk
Turn on the desk lamp
anns.task_desc: Pick up a tennis racket and turn on a lamp

high_descs: Turn left then walk straight to the wood desk where the tennis racket is sitting on the ground
Pick up the tennis racket sitting on the floor against the desk
Carry the tennis racket to the small wood night stand where the lamp is
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry a tennis racket while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk to the desk.
Pick up the tennis racket leaning against the side of the desk.
Turn around, walk to the small night stand with the lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: View the tennis racket in the light.

high_descs: Turn left and move towards the end of the desk that has a laptop on it.
Pick up the tennis racket on the floor next to the desk.
Turn left and move towards the small dresser that has a lamp on top of it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket using the light of a lamp.
